snippet.title: AgileDevArt
snippet.description:
Welcome to AgileDevArt !

On this channel you will find tutorials on how to create 3D and 2D art as used in games, C# programing patterns and tips and also behind the scenes development videos from the creator of the game called Snappy Mouse Run.

App Store:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/snappy-mouse-run/id1163515281

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.agiledevart.snap

Amazon Store:
http://www.amazon.com/gp/mas/dl/android?asin=B07J15TS3R

Stay inspired :)
